tributes to the larger historical debate and\nprovides useful input to the wide and varied range of evidence that has to be\ndebated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 17:33:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 29 Apr 2017 15:16:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-02"}
