nt\ncommunication and self-triggered communication with centralized and\ndecentralized sensor fusion) through simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 21:57:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 14:33:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-24"}
