se results, we recommend that\naveraging BOLD signals over anatomically defined ROIs should be carefully\nconsidered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2017 11:23:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-10"}
