 eruptions. We suggest that the\ndifferences in the deflection and rotation of the CMEs can explain whether each\nCME impacted or missed the Earth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2017 13:42:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-21"}
